item.title: Help on port forwarding
item.dc:creator: @ectophantom ectophantom
item.description:
@ectophantom wrote:

for the network connection details type 192.168.1.1 in you web browser, it might need a password which is probably

username:admin
password:admin

or

username:admin
password:password

dont worry, no one else can access this.[br][size=1]Posted on: September 15, 2007, 09:26:48 PM[/size][hr]and you do put your static ip, but for other people to play on your server, you need to give them your internet IP, if you dont know where to find your IP goto http://www.ipchicken.com/ and it will tell you in big blue numbers =P
